casebody.data:
WHITTEMORE, Respondent, v. WHITE et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

June 19, 1893.) Action by Henry Whittemore against James T. White and others. Oscar J. Hochstadter, for appellants. Gilbert R. Hawes, for respondent. '

No opinion. Motion for reargument. Reargument granted. Stay meanwhile. See 23 N. Y. Supp. 1161.
